Not coming back
A La Carte was one of my favorite hotels when visiting Danang. Had previously stayed back in 2017 & 2019 and had a wonderful experience in the past. I decided to give it another try. Unfortunately, my family had mixed experiences during the check-in process. In my case, a friendly bellman greeted me, and the gentleman at the reception desk did a great job getting me checked in. At that time, I did provide my entire family's documents to confirm our check-in process. However, my wife, a local to Danang, did experience a different level of hospitality upon entering the building that I, unfortunately, had to witness primarily by the bellman not allowing her to even hit the elevator area without speaking with the front desk. She attempted to explain to them that she was already‚Ä¶
Date of stay: May 2023
