Rohit S wrote a review Jan 2023
New Delhi, India21 contributions
Large Oceanside rooms
Hotel is full of Large spacious clean rooms. Suggest to take 2 bedroom apartment if with kids. Location also good, just opposite the ocean. My family had a great time each morning playing with the ocean tides. Me being vegan, had a tough time in breakfast. Need to improve vegan items in menu. Also kids play area very small, not really a play area. Swimming pool is good if weather is hot, but not heated in case of cold weather Overall service good.
Date of stay: January 2023
